full_text: Professional help is not a sign of weakness. Let's unmute ourself, speak up, ask for help & not to suffer in a silo. I urge everyone not to mock people. Bullying can have devastating effects on one's mental health. Be kind. Let's make this world a safe place for everyone.  8/8
full_text(utf-8): b"Professional help is not a sign of weakness. Let's unmute ourself, speak up, ask for help & not to suffer in a silo. I urge everyone not to mock people. Bullying can have devastating effects on one's mental health. Be kind. Let's make this world a safe place for everyone.  8/8"

full_text: So because of lack of awareness, stigma & fear of being judged by others my depression went untreated for 6 years. Now I'm doing my bit increase mental health awareness in society. People don't require mental illness to take care of mental health. 7/n
full_text(utf-8): b"So because of lack of awareness, stigma & fear of being judged by others my depression went untreated for 6 years. Now I'm doing my bit increase mental health awareness in society. People don't require mental illness to take care of mental health. 7/n"

full_text: Daily I have to deal with crushing pain of anxiety & depression. However, I know with professional help things will improve with time. 6/n
full_text(utf-8): b'Daily I have to deal with crushing pain of anxiety & depression. However, I know with professional help things will improve with time. 6/n'

full_text: Again I choose to suffer for 2 years. In 2019, I was in ICU for 14 hours with terminally ill patients. I thought about life & decided to take professional help. Then, I was diagnosed with depression & anxiety disorder. Now, I'm taking treatment from the past 15 months.  5/n

full_text: I had a bad experience with my 1st job in Ahmedabad. I choose to suffer in absence of any help from society. In 2017, I left my job for exam preparation & came back to Jaipur. Even for months, I was not able to study. My mental health deteriorated. 4/n

full_text: He was nice & helped me with academic issues. However, he was not able to diagnose depression. In college, people consider counselling as a sign of weakness. 3/n

full_text:
Happy Independence Day!

Let us also remember 'Fundamental Duties ' while exercising 'Fundamental Rights'.

Personally, I want the freedom to discuss mental health issues without stigma & fear of being judged.
